<h1>What is BoatHouse Pictures?</h1>

<p>BoatHouse Pictures is located in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. Here at BHP we focus on the production and development of original motion pictures. Our film projects range from shorts, using local talents, to larger scale feature films. Our goal is to provide entertaining, creative, and original movies. For upcoming features, click here.</p>

<p>BHP seeks to focus not only on movies, but by connecting with our community and making a difference right here at home. Keeping this in mind, we provide services for our local (Tri-State) businesses and consumers. These services range from videography, industrial shorts, commercials, and event coverage, For more information about our services, please visit our "Services" Tab. </p> 

<h1>Our Crew:</h1>
<p>Our crew is made up of talented and passionate individuals from different academic and professional backgrounds, coming together for one central goal... success. Our success is measured by the products we provide and how we please our consumers.</p>

