<p><strong>Andre Saballette – Executive Director</strong><p>
<p>Andre Saballette is the creative mind behind the philosophy, goals, and standard for the company. He has been working in the film industry, both in front and behind the cameras, since late 2008. In the few years since his career began, he has worked on a diverse range of projects which include feature length narratives, documentaries, shorts, industrial, and commercials.</p>

<p>Immediately prior to Boathouse Pictures, Andre Saballette worked for the Walt Disney Company, where he strengthened his creative skills; as well as, shaped the values he brought to Boathouse Pictures, which include high production quality and customer satisfaction. It is the experienced and skills acquired with the Walt Disney Company, along with the philosophy inspired by one of his biggest idols, Walt Disney himself, which has allowed Andre Saballette to shape the company, organizing productions, networking, and increasing the chances for high profitability.</p>

<p>He holds a Bachelor of Arts in Liberal Arts with a Minor in film, from Penn State University and is currently pursuing an MBA in Management and Economics.</p>

