<p><strong>Aaron Spence – Director of Special Projects & Logistics</strong></p>
<p>Aaron Spence brings with him years of experience in small business logistics and organizational management that will help make our operation much more efficient.</p>

<p>Aaron currently serves as the Director of Special Operations for BoatHouse Pictures. In that capacity, he supervises the logistical needs for clients large and small while also managing the day to day operations of the company. He is a proud graduate of both West Philadelphia Catholic High School and La Salle University. Aaron serves on the boards of several local community organizations including the West Catholic Alumni Association Board of Governors, The Overbrook Park Church of Christ, The Nubians House,and The HER Project, where he serves as Chairman of the Boa.</p>

